Class Manager

java.lang.Object
com.example.theaterproject.Models.Account
com.example.theaterproject.Models.Manager
public class Manager extends Account
Represents a manager user in the theater project system.

This class extends Account and inherits its authentication-related fields and behaviors. A Manager is essentially a specialized type of Account with additional privileges for managing theater operations.
